Coin Cpecifications 
POW/POS Hybrid
Algo: Nist 5
Name: Bitspace
Ticker: BSX
Block time: 60 seconds
POW block reward: 100 BSX
Last POW block: 450010
Block maturity: 30 blocks
POS starts from block:1
POS yearly interest: 10%
Min. stake age: 24 hours
Max. stake age: unlimited
Decimal places: 8
Min. sending fee: 0.00001 BSX
Premine : 10% (reserved for ICO)
RPC Port: 13250
P2P Port: 13252

Distribution

Bitspace is a POW/POS hybrid 
POW and POS starts from 1st block.
POW block reward is constant 100 BSX per block.
POS interest is 10% early.
POW mining phase will last for one year. And It will end at block 450 010.  
After POW ends. Bitspace will be auto switched to pure POS.
